manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "m_rust"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "m_rust"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
rust-version = "1.71.0"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
dotenvy = "0.15.7"
dotenvy_macro = "0.15.7"
serde = "1.0.177"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.26"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.rocket]
version = "0.5.0-rc.3"
features = ["tls", "json", "secrets"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.7"
features = ["runtime-tokio", "tls-native-tls", "postgres", "chrono"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.29.1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.4.1"
features = ["v4"]
